---
title: Jerk Black Bean Bowl & Spiced Wedges with Toasted Coconut & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Tonight, put together a bountiful bowl full of Caribbean flavours! With spiced black beans, zingy lemon yoghurt, potato wedges and a cucumber salsa, every bite of this bright meal is as good as the next!
